name: Curious Antlers
description: Venture out in to the wild to witness such eventful scenes. Look how curious they are when they spot you, the next moment they just vanish. Masinagudi is a great destination where you get to see herds of Chital or Spotted Deer and Chital stags with their gorgeous antlers. The rutting calls of the Chital stags announcing their presence reverberates through the forests.
